## Register External Agents

External agents in any language implement 3 endpoints (`/analyze`, `/challenge`, `/vote`):

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/agents \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name": "my_agent", "domain": "code analysis", "base_url": "http://my-agent:3000"}'
```
